In re Resignation of Anderson.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Anderson (1992), 63 Ohio St.3d 1209.]

(No. 92-176 Submitted March 17, 1992 Decided April 1, 1992.)

The resignation of Delores Joan Anderson as an attorney, Registration No. 0023114, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
